*splashutils-1.5.4.4 (30 Aug 2011)

  30 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +splashutils-1.5.4.4.ebuild, -splashutils-1.1.9.10-r8.ebuild,
  +files/splashutils-1.5.4.4-clip.patch, +files/splash,
  +files/splashutils-1.5.4.4-gentoo-typo-fix.patch,
  +files/splashutils-1.5.4.4-freetype-bz2.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-2.6.18-vt-fix.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-fr.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-mountopts.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-ppc-2.6.14.patch,
  -files/splashutils-depscan.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-types_h.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-makefile.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-mountsilent.patch,
  -files/splashutils-1.1.9.10-roroot.patch:
  Bump to latest. Merge all clip patches into a single one.
  Bumped libpng, freetype and zlib distfiles to latest ones in CLIP.
  Added a '/sbin/splash' wrapper script to provide backward compatibility
  with CLIP init scripts.
  Add SYS_TTY_CONFIG inheritable cap to fbsplashd.static.

